Rating: 4
This was one of the easiest recipes I have EVER made, and definitely one of the most delicious. I only had two pieces of veal to cook, but we managed to eat all of the sauce with no problem at all. It was especially good served over brown rice. If I were to make this for more people, I would probably double the sauce recipe. Overall, this was a simple recipe that tastes like you spent hours in the kitchen. I will definitely make this again.

Rating: 3
This was a good dish. I made it with chicken, and suggest you pound it thin. I dusted the chicken with season salt mixture and Italian herb before cooking them. Also, the butter mixture that you cook the mushrooms in is best to reserve to use to cook the chicken/veal in with EVOO.

